  ID: MalteseSoldier2
  Name: Fra Jean, noble knight
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "He rehearsed his death as poetry, something sculpted by faith. Gangrene
    has no interest in poetry \u2014 the black progresses up his leg despite prayer.
    He asks for the blade, not benediction.\n\nTreatment: Saw above the blackened
    flesh. If infection has already spread into blood, nothing changes. If he refuses
    surgery, the dagger ends the waiting. His choice, not yours."
